=slide :about do
  :markdown
    Ekylibre is a farming ERP distributed under GNU GPL v3 license. It includes following modules:

      - Relationship management
      - Accountancy
      - Sales, purchases, and stocks
      - Production management and traceability
      - User-based access control

    It's an web application based on [Ruby on Rails](http://rubyonrails.org).

